<html xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' xmlns:w='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word'><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>IELTS Answers</title></head><body><h1>DAILY ROUTINE ANSWERS</h1><h3>Câu 1: Can you tell me about your typical morning routine?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> When do you wake up ? (at + thời gian).<br>6 am every morning. <br>How do you feel ?.<br>I often feel tired when i wake early.<br>Why do you wake up so early ?.<br>I have a lot of works to do. wake up to prepare for a day.<br>What do you do in your bedroom ?.<br>do + gì đó -> dọn dẹp và làm (do my bed, do my hair, check my phone for any news, listen to weather forecast...).<br>Then i go to the bathroom. (what ?.)<br>wash face, brush my teeth, have body spray, shave beer. <br>do not have a morning shower.<br>Go downstari to the kitchen. (what ?.)<br>I open my fridge, have some ingredients to make my breakfast.<br>What do you have for breakfast ?.<br>-> light meal like some loads of bread, grains.<br>What do you have for a drink ?.<br>-> warm water -> to hydrate. <br>Do you prefer a tea or a coffee ?.<br>I prefer coffee -> the mixture of coffee and milk always make my day. <br>a quarter to seven. <br>How do you get to work ?.<br>bike -> How far/ how long ? only 5 minutues to get there. It is very convinient.<br>Why motorbike but not other vehicles ?.<br>-> bicyle -> because it took longer to ride to workplace. It is physical demanding.  <br>-> car -> it is unaffordable -> but i have a plan to one in the future.<br>What is your current job ?.<br>-> I'm working at  import company which distribute the oil to mechanical machine. <br>What is your position ?.<br>-> I am a sale exclusive. <br>-> I make a phone call to potential customers and cater (v): chăm sóc their requests.<br>What do you like about your job ?.<br>-> 1. The thing i like most about my jobs is that i can go to many places in my countries, meet and connect with new people. (travel).<br>-> 2. salary -> the salary is rewarding/ lucrative/high<br>-> 3. potential.<br>What do you hate about your job ?.<br>-> 1. The job is time-demanding. I have to be "on-call" to service my customers. I have to sacrifire my private time and work-life balance.<br><br><br><br> <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 2: What do you usually have for breakfast?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you love cooking ?.<br>Yes, in some aspects<br>When do you cook ? -> I often cook for dinner. <br>Why do you cooking ?. <br>1. i think cooking is relaxing. <br>2. I manage the nutritions and product orgin, personal flavour. I cook the dishes that i love.<br>What dishes do you usually cook ?.<br>I am a beef steak lover. to cook a beef steak you need a certain skills. You have to master the fire control, timing. <br>Can you tell me how to make smoothies ?.<br>I think smoothies is easy to make but it is not my favour. <br>How to make fried egg ?.<br>-> first, i must have a egg basket from the supermarket. <br>-> then, i break three or four egg depending on personal portion. <br>-> mix them with onions and a pinch of salt. <br>-> prepare and heat the pan. <br>-> put some oil and the mixed egg on heated pan.<br>-> wait for 3 minutes and enjoy !.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br> </p><hr><h3>Câu 4: Do you like going out for a short walk?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you like going out for a short walk?<br>-> Yes, I often go jogging. when/where do you go jogging<br>When ? From Monday to Friday, I am busy with my works so i often go jogging at 5.0 pm or at the weekend. <br>Where (how far/ how long) ? I go jogging at the park -> It is near my house. It only takes me 10 minutes to get there on foot.<br>What does the park have ?. (miêu tả)<br>-> The park is a large place, have lots space. It has a lake in the middle, dirt path, trees, gardens surround . It is a noisy and crowded in the morning but quite peaceful in the evening.<br>What do you often do in the park ?<br>-> 1. I usually sit on the chair under the shade and enjoy some tea. <br>-> 2. rent a pedalo on the lake.<br>-> 3. do some excerices with the equipements.<br>Do you love shopping ?.(when/where/why)<br>-> Yes, i am shopping lover. (yêu thích). I often shop for basic products, new models, figures, tech devices, ... at the weekend when i earn my salary at the shopping malls. <br>Do you prefer to shop at tradditional market or supermarket ?.<br>-> supermarket. <br>I would love to shop at supermarket. <br>1. Nhiều đồ (nhiều lựa chọn về kích thước, chất liệu, giá cả, ...)<br>It has various products. This mean More options to choose in size, types, prices, ...<br>2. Có thẻ giá trên sản phẩm (không phải mặc cả).<br>-> It always has price tags on the products so i do not have bargain. . <br>3. Có điều hòa. It has air condition. It is cool in the summer and warm in the winter.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>Do you often meet your friends ?<br>-> ____ -> __ -> ____ off from works.<br>When ? From Monday Friday at the weekend/ when i have time or money ?. <br>Why do you love shopping ?<br>Why do you traveling ?<br>Why do you love book ?<br>Why do you love movies ?<br>-> entertainment.<br>-> learn. <br>-> family<br>1. -> This is my hobby. It is relaxing (entertainment) <br>2. -> Do you prefer to shop alone or with your friends. It create memories that last forever.  (family) <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br> <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br> </p><hr><h3>Câu 10: Do you like going out for a drink or eating out?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you like going out for a drink or eating out ?.<br>I really like going out with friends, especially for a date. <br>When/where -> Me and my friends live in different cities so we often hang out at the weekend or on special occasions. <br>Where do you often go out ?. -> I ofen choose restaurants for meal, and coffee shop for a drink to go with friends.<br>Why do you choose the coffee shop ?.<br>1. không gian -> the coffee shop offers airy space. It does not have many people so it is crowded.   <br>2. âm nhạc -> The place has relaxing music like piano, trendy songs, .. <br>3. đồ uống -> The most special thing about the coffee is the drinks, they have various menu in types from coffee to smoothies, juices, ... <br><br><br><br><br> </p><hr><h3>Câu 11: Where and When do you usually meet your friends?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you love books ?. <br>I am a book lovers. I love novels and comics. <br>Why do you love books.<br>1. entertainmet (It is my hobby. for me, reading new stories from novels or comics is really entertaining because it allows my mind to rest and relax after stressful day at work).<br>2. learn. (Books also contain practical knowledge to apply in casual life. VD: Cooking books teach me how to make my favourite dishes, ... <br>Nutrition book tell you the proper way to manage your eating habbit, ...<br><br></p><hr></body></html>